   - Component block pricing: 3 alike components = 60G instead of 3×25=75G
   - Claim processing: deductible 100G per item, cap 2× insurance sum, enchantment ≥8 reimburse 50%, dragon material full reimbursement, "both clauses: 50% rule wins"
